; Proxy dxgi.dll — Fallout 4 NG imports CreateDXGIFactory only, but we
; forward all three factory-creation entry points for robustness against
; plugins that resolve via GetProcAddress.
;
; All 3 forward to the real dxgi.dll loaded from %SYSTEMROOT%\System32
; (see proxy_exports.cpp). No __declspec(dllexport) in sources — .def is
; authoritative.
;
; Why dxgi.dll and not dinput8.dll? Pre-NG FO4 imported dinput8 directly,
; so the community "dinput8 proxy" pattern worked. NG (1.10.980+) removed
; that import — Fallout4.exe now imports XINPUT1_3 + dxgi + d3d11. dxgi
; is the lowest DLL in the DX11 stack and is guaranteed loaded at startup.
LIBRARY "dxgi"
EXPORTS
    CreateDXGIFactory
    CreateDXGIFactory1
    CreateDXGIFactory2
